title: What We Learned From Week 6 in the N.F.L.
description: Josh Allen was ready for Kansas City’s blitzes, the Jets exposed the Packers’ defense, and Tom Brady’s rift with the Buccaneers’ offensive line is growing.
dc:creator: Derrik Klassen
media:credit: Denny Medley/USA Today Sports, via Reuters
media:description: Bills quarterback Josh Allen leaped over a defender as Buffalo toppled Kansas City, 24-20, Sunday.
